nodes.text: Back at the Ranch was a department of Star Wars Galaxy Collector magazine that provided a behind-the-scenes look at developments going on at Lucasfilm's Skywalker Ranch during the lead up to the theatrical release Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace.
Star Wars Galaxy Collector 1: "Gavin Bocquet: Building A Galaxy, Board By Board"
Examining the role of Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace Production Designer Gavin Bocquet
